            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a full kettle</p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>in 700ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[975ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, then add your<strong> tomato paste</strong>, <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>and <strong>chilli relish</strong> – this is your<strong> sweet tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1679830137548-x200.jpg",
