            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>arborio rice</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>ground turmeric</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min further</p><p>Add 1/3 of the <strong>sweet tomato stock</strong> and stir continuously until absorbed</p><p>Continue to add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>sweet tomato stock</strong>, a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 25-30 min, until all the stock is absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>risotto</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
