      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, top the<strong> chicken, pepper & chive risotto </strong>with the <strong>reserved roasted pepper</strong> and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped chives</strong> and a<strong> </strong>drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
